og:title: OneKey® MLS Launches RentSpree Integration for All Subscribers
ogDescription: OneKey® MLS's new integration with RentSpree’s platform will streamline rental transactions. All OneKey MLS subscribers will have access to RentSpree’s ApplyLink™ for new and existing rental listings to cut down transaction time, limit liability, increase efficiency, and keep agents central to the rental transaction.
